  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>ABOUT THE GAME</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Secret Story 1996</strong> is a first-person narrative horror game partially inspired by real events, featuring multiple story paths shaped by your choices.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>STORY</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as <strong>Serena</strong>, a young woman who runs away from home in search of a new hope. But what begins as a quiet night in an old hotel slowly turns into a desperate struggle for survival. As midnight approaches, Serena must face the truth, confront her fears, and choose a path that may change her fate forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>GAME FEATURE</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1996 visuals and atmosphere</strong> <br> Step into the world of an old 1990s hotel, filled with dark, uneasy atmosphere and a stronger narrative presentation.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367740/extras/dddb279413fb85451a49f5eaa4c6b010.poster.avif?t=1774466211\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367740/extras/dddb279413fb85451a49f5eaa4c6b010.webm?t=1774466211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367740/extras/dddb279413fb85451a49f5eaa4c6b010.mp4?t=1774466211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Branching story paths (free updates planned)</strong> <br>Every choice matters. Your decisions can change the course of the story and lead to different outcomes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367740/extras/0c39617e76fd7da20c0ccda6b8cf6b09.poster.avif?t=1774466211\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367740/extras/0c39617e76fd7da20c0ccda6b8cf6b09.webm?t=1774466211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367740/extras/0c39617e76fd7da20c0ccda6b8cf6b09.mp4?t=1774466211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Varied gameplay and activities</strong> <br> Experience first-person gameplay with interactive mechanics, NPC encounters, and hotel activities that bring the world of 1996 to life.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367740/extras/95031c34208ac4d03a26c1eca56dc9f0.poster.avif?t=1774466211\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367740/extras/95031c34208ac4d03a26c1eca56dc9f0.webm?t=1774466211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367740/extras/95031c34208ac4d03a26c1eca56dc9f0.mp4?t=1774466211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Subtitle</strong> <strong>Story 3 language support</strong>  <br> The story can be played in English, Thai, and Chinese.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367740/extras/cd8085bc584856b6daafa9c2fe56e2ae.avif?t=1774466211\" width=780 height=438 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><u><strong>A Note from the Developer</strong></u></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This project is being developed entirely by a solo developer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for your patience and support. Every part of the game from story, design, gameplay, atmosphere, to presentation  has been created and refined with care by one person.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The remake into <strong>The Secret Story 1996</strong> marks the beginning of a new direction for this project, and the game will continue to be improved in the future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you enjoy the game and would like to support its growth, your purchase, feedback, and review truly mean a lot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for love my game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>UDAGamelab</strong> </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>ABOUT THE GAME</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Secret Story 1996</strong> is a first-person narrative horror game partially inspired by real events, featuring multiple story paths shaped by your choices.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>STORY</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as <strong>Serena</strong>, a young woman who runs away from home in search of a new hope. But what begins as a quiet night in an old hotel slowly turns into a desperate struggle for survival. As midnight approaches, Serena must face the truth, confront her fears, and choose a path that may change her fate forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>GAME FEATURE</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1996 visuals and atmosphere</strong> <br> Step into the world of an old 1990s hotel, filled with dark, uneasy atmosphere and a stronger narrative presentation.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367740/extras/dddb279413fb85451a49f5eaa4c6b010.poster.avif?t=1774466211\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367740/extras/dddb279413fb85451a49f5eaa4c6b010.webm?t=1774466211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3367740/extras/dddb279413fb85451a49f5eaa4c6b010.mp4?t=1774466211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Branching story paths (free updates planned)</strong> <br>Every choice matters. Your decisions can change the course of the story and lead to different outcomes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><spa