 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><u><strong>A Note from the Developer</strong></u></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This project is being developed entirely by a solo developer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for your patience and support. Every part of the game from story, design, gameplay, atmosphere, to presentation  has been created and refined with care by one person.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The remake into <strong>The Secret Story 1996</strong> marks the beginning of a new direction for this project, and the game will continue to be improved in the future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you enjoy the game and would like to support its growth, your purchase, feedback, and review truly mean a lot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for love my game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>UDAGamelab</strong> </p>",
